bio.openEndedText: Hi!! Welcome to my newest  entrepreneurial idea, Turo Rentals!  Adding our fleet of cars to our Short Term Rental (Airbnb/Vrbo Houses) has been a dream of mine for 2 years, we love hosting people in our houses and now we are hosting people in our cars!  Thanks for choosing us and please send us a note with any questions anytime!

Exceptional customer service is THE top priority. 
See other cars in the fleet at www.CarsByJ.com

Locally owned and operated car rental company serving the city of Cleveland, Ohio. Our goal is to provide reliable and affordable transportation options for individuals and families in the area.

Why rent from me?
3000+ trips, with great reviews 
One of Turo's "All-Star" Hosts (Only 5-10% of Turo hosts qualify for this distinction)
Also have been given the distinction of “Power Host”
Instant booking (no need to wait for approval) for Home Location 
Cars available for pick-up/drop off 9am-9pm through contactless check-in
Same day bookings available
I don’t have any papers to sign.
You have confidence in knowing if you book it; it will be available. I have not canceled any trips for any reasons ever. 
Flexibility: If you need to drop the car off early it's no problem. Request the change in Turo. If you need it another few hours or days it's no problem as long as there are no other trips booked after yours. Turo will allow you to request a change as long as there are no other trips and I have approved all changes requested. 

Thank you for taking the time to read my profile,
Rich A

Hi, my name is Vitaliy I’m from Ukraine and I’ve been running a customer service oriented business for 15 years.  With this flawless track record I am now hosting your car ride.  Absolutely love customer satisfaction as it’s the greatest reward of being in business.

We are dedicated to providing our customers with an exceptional and memorable driving experience. Our mission is to offer a fleet of pristine, top-quality luxury and affordable vehicles, coupled with unmatched customer service. We aim to cater to the desires of discerning individuals who seek not just transportation,  but a statement of their refined taste and style.  We have vehicles that can meet every budget, and are able to accommodate parties of two or twelve individuals. Thank you for considering our vehicles you will not be disappointed.
